Uses of Package
com.skobbler.ngx

Packages that use com.skobbler.ngx
com.skobbler.ngx Contains classes needed for initializing the SKMaps framework. 
com.skobbler.ngx.map Constains classses needed to show the map and information on the map. 
com.skobbler.ngx.map.realreach Contains classes needed to for implement RealReach feature. 
com.skobbler.ngx.navigation Contains classes needed for making a turn by turn navigation. 
com.skobbler.ngx.poitracker Contains classes for tracking pois during navigation. 
com.skobbler.ngx.positioner Contains classes used for implementing a positioner. 
com.skobbler.ngx.positioner.logging   
com.skobbler.ngx.reversegeocode Contains classes that are needed in order to make a reverse geocode. 
com.skobbler.ngx.routing Contains classes that are needed in order to make a route and information about the status of computed routes. 
com.skobbler.ngx.search Contains classes needed to make a search (Nearby search , Multistep search). 
com.skobbler.ngx.trail Contains classses needed to show trails 
com.skobbler.ngx.util Constains utility classes
